CSS -> Cascading Style Sheet -> Default stylesheet for HTML Document (Webpages)

SASS -> LESS -> CSS -> 
3 Ways of usage: Inline | Internal | External

CSS Syntax: For Internal and External
selector {
    property: value; -> Rule 1
    property: value; -> Rule 2
}

selector: Name selector(h1, p, ul, img) | ID selector(#id_name) | Class selector(.class_name)

h1 {
    background-color: white;
}

